    "biography": "<p>A reclusive mining spirit (a knocker or rapper) that haunts mountains and mines, glamouring its territory and triggering 'accidental' rockfalls to drive off intruders.</p><p><strong>Powers:</strong> Accident (Zone), Control Resistance, Enhanced Physical Attributes (Strength & Body, 4×/day for [Essence×Essence] turns), Enhanced Senses (Low-Light Vision, Thermographic Vision), Fading, Glamour (Zone ×4; negate with TN [3×Essence]+2), Magic Sense, Magical Resistance, Masking</p><p><strong>Weaknesses:</strong> Allergy (Sunlight, Severe)</p><p><em>Attacks: 6L, Reach −1. Habitat: Inside mountains and hills, inside mines. Range: Throughout Europe. Avoids all contact with (meta)humanity. Some possess shamanic talents (earth/mountain spirits). Book Intelligence 3/5. PAE p.119.</em></p>",
